    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To go to the declaration of a symbol, press <code>Ctrl + B</code>. For example, pressing this on a variable will take the cursor to the variable declaration.</p>\n<p>Using it on a class name will open a new tab and take you to the class file. With <code>⌥ + ⌘ + B</code> on <code>MacOS</code> and  <code>Ctrl+Alt+B</code> on [<code>Windows/Linux</code>], you can navigate to an <code>implementation</code> too.</p>\n"
